Building lava-tool
==================

For unstable:
-------------

$ gbp buildpackage

For jessie backports:
---------------------

Uses a jessie-backports schroot.
Change <KEYID> and <VERSION> for your GnuPG Debian key and the most recent
version of lava-tool in backports.

$ gbp buildpackage --git-debian-branch=backports \
  --git-builder=sbuild -d jessie-backports -A -s --force-orig-source \
  --debbuildopts='-v<VERSION>' -k<KEYID>

